                        "name": "twk",
                        "displayName": "twk",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/code\/browse\/Zend_Framework\/standard\/branches\/release-1.8\/documentation\/manual\/en\/module_specs\/Zend_Controller-Migration.xml?r=15464#l20\n\n> the <code>@<\/code> character is no a special character in the beginning of a route segment.\nYou mean \"*now* a special character\"?\n",
